==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: There is no person that has 1000 good days (in a row), and no flower that stays red for 100 days.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: rén wú qīan rì hăo, hūa wú băi rì hóng

===Phrase===
'''[[人]][[无]][[千]][[日]][[好]]，[[花]][[无]][[百]][[日]][[红]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') Nothing good lasts forever; all good things must come to an end.

===Alternate forms===
[[人]][[無]][[千]][[日]][[好]]，[[花]][[無]][[百]][[日]][[紅]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

